data.description: Experience the epitome of coastal living in this split-level oasis in Harbor Island's coveted Ocean Marsh neighborhood. Enjoy lagoon views from the front porch, and marsh/canal views from the various back decks, one of which features an automated canopy. The main level boasts a spacious din/kit/liv combo with vaulted ceilings, built in bookshelves, custom oak cabinetry, built in pantry, and granite countertops. The master suite features an ensuite bath and private deck overlooking the scenic canal. This home exudes comfort and and sophistication with two guest bedrooms, hardwood flooring, and numerous upgrades!
